       +-----------------+
       |   Frontend UI   |
       |  (React App)    |
       |-----------------|
       | - Login/Signup  |
       | - Wallets       |
       | - Orders        |
       | - Trade Feed    |
       +--------+--------+
                |
          REST API Calls
                |
                v
       +-----------------+
       |   Backend API   |
       |  (FastAPI)      |
       |-----------------|
       | - Auth          |
       | - Wallets       |
       | - Orders        |
       | - Trades        |
       +--------+--------+
                |
        WebSocket Updates
                |
                v
       +-----------------+
       | Real-time Feed  |
       | (Orders/Trades) |
       +--------+--------+
                |
                v
       +-----------------+
       |   Database      |
       | (Postgres)      |
       |-----------------|
       | - Users         |
       | - Wallets       |
       | - Orders        |
       | - Trades        |
       +-----------------+



   ┌───────────────┐           ┌───────────────┐
   │   API Client  │  HTTP     │   FastAPI     │
   │ (browser/app) │ ────────> │   Endpoint   │
   └───────────────┘           └───────────────┘
                                        │
                                        │ validates input
                                        ▼
                              ┌───────────────────┐
                              │  Pydantic Model   │
